Short intro to Leon's documentation
===================================

Install Sphinx (http://sphinx.pocoo.org/):

1. Install Python 2.4 or higher
2. Install Sphinx using the following command: easy_install -U Sphinx
3. Make sure you have installed make

Done!


Generating html documentation
-----------------------------

* make html

The output can be found in the _build directory.


Generating pdf documentation
----------------------------

* Install a LaTeX distribution
* run: make latexpdf
